## Code Standards

### Language

- **Code/Commits/Docs**: Always English

### Commits

Always commit progress after completing a task.

```
<type>(<scope>): <description>

feat(api): add fleet CRUD endpoints
fix(web): resolve component import
docs: update project documentation
```

### Prohibited

- Task-specific comments
- `console.log` in production
- Commented-out code
- Magic numbers

